Y_k
N\sim(a_k,\sigma^2)
\bar Y=\sum_{k=1}^{n}\frac{Y_k}{n}
S^2
\frac{(n-1)S^2}{\sigma^2}=\frac{1}{\sigma^2}\sum_{k=1}^{n}(Y_k-\bar Y)^2
\chi^2
(n-1)
\lambda=\sum_{k=1}^n\frac{(a_k-\bar a)^2}{\sigma^2}
\bar a=\sum_{k=1}^{n}\frac{a_k}{n}
Y
P
(Y_1,\ldots, Y_n)^T
x_1=\cdots=x_n
Q=I-P
(n-1)
x_1+\cdots+x_n=0
x_1=\cdots=x_n
 Q\begin{bmatrix} Y_1 \\  \vdots \\ Y_n \end{bmatrix} = \begin{bmatrix} Y_1-\bar Y \\  \vdots \\ Y_n-\bar Y \end{bmatrix} \text{ and }Q\begin{bmatrix} a_1 \\  \vdots \\ a_n \end{bmatrix} = \begin{bmatrix} a_1-\bar a \\  \vdots \\ a_n-\bar a \end{bmatrix}. 
 Q\begin{bmatrix} U_1 \\ U_2 \\  \vdots \\ U_n \end{bmatrix} = \begin{bmatrix} 0 \\ U_2 \\  \vdots \\ U_n \end{bmatrix} \text{ and }Q\begin{bmatrix} b_1 \\ b_2 \\  \vdots \\ b_n \end{bmatrix} = \begin{bmatrix} 0 \\ b_2 \\  \vdots \\ b_n \end{bmatrix}. 
 \frac{1}{\sigma^2}(U_2^2+\cdots +U_n^2) \sim \chi^2_{n-1,b_2^2+\cdots+b_n^2}. 
 (Y_1-\bar Y)^2 + \cdots+(Y_n-\bar Y)^2 = U_2^2+\cdots+U_n^2 
 (a_1-\bar a)^2+\cdots+(a_n-\bar a)^2 = b_2^2+\cdots+b_n^2. 
